dspace.title: Please release content listed in the attached spreadsheet from the OAR this Monday (10/28)

comments.body:
While the NetIDs are accessible for some of the authors from the Symplectic Elements installation (hosted on oaworkflow.princeton.edu), I am currently working to troubleshoot the following error I encounter when I attempt to release publications by author NetID:

```
dspace@oar-prod-repo: master item-release> ./quickArchiveAuthors mbattagl@princeton.edu
...
*** Keeping traces in logs/./quickArchiveAuthors-9630
Exception: DataSource edu.princeton.oar.FacultyUrlDataSource@6535ef24: null
java.lang.RuntimeException: DataSource edu.princeton.oar.FacultyUrlDataSource@6535ef24: null
```

It may be the case that this error indicates that the author cannot be retrieved within the database using the specified NetID (i. e. I am using the wrong NetID or ID for the author with this script), or, there may be some other cause for this. I am seeking out assistance in resolving this.
